README

The coupler is a package for parallel data transfer between arbitrary physics codes.

SETUP
-----

Run the 'setup_nemesis' script to configure vendors.

Runt the 'coupler_config' script to generate autoconf configure files.

CONFIGURE
---------

See './configure --help' for configure options.

BUILD
-----

make - Standard build.

make check - Standard build with unit tests.

make autodoc - Generate doxygen documentation.
